5:
Ahhh, it's good to be back on
Paradise Isle!
8:
Oh, that reminds me, Light said he
wants to master swimming this time
for sure. Think you could be my
teaching assistant?
17:
Hey, you guys seen Azel at all? He
WAS on the boat with us, but he's up
and vanished since then.
20: U-um... Like I said, I'm fine.
22:
Don't be like that, babe! We don't
mind carrying your bags!
25:
Yeah, sweetheart, why don't you
hand 'em over and tell us where
you're headed? We can show you a
REAL good time.
33:
There seems to be a problem here.
Perhaps I can offer my assistance?
38:
Abs...olutely not! We were just
headed out! Anyway, b-b-biceps—I
mean, bye!
41:
Uh... Yeah, for their sakes, I'm gonna
pretend I didn't see that...
45: Alk, Nimbus! Apologies for the wait!
58:
Feigning ignorance at your friend's
greeting is very rude, Alk.
61:
S-sorry, but... Can you blame me?
You look totally different!
68:
I noticed a number of eyes on me
on my way here... I've never worn a
swimsuit before, so perhaps I am
ill-suited to such attire?
72:
Not at all! Quite the opposite,
actually...
76:
A-anyway! You said this is your first
time at a resort like this, right?
78:
Is there anything you want to do?
We can definitely show you around.
85:
I have to admit, I'm not accustomed
to this sort of leisure, so I think I will
simply follow your lead.
87: As long as you don't mind.
91:
Sure! In that case, what do you
wanna do first, Stella?
103: Hold on tight, okay? Ready, and...
110: Jeez, that really sent you flying.
115:
Yes, it did. But for a brief moment... I
was speed.
119:
Quite the wild stallion we have here.
But once we break him in, he should
make a fine steed.
123: Wonderful, Stella! How do you feel?!
126: The wind! It's like I'm riding the wind!
137:
We're lagging too far behind! Alk,
take the wheel and stay the course!
I shall—
140:
H-hey, Mr. Hot Shot! We're here to
pay you back for before!
142:
W-we challenge you to a race! If we
win, you come with us and explain
to that cute girl it was all a misunde—
144:
Apologies, but we do not have time
for silly games! This is an
emergency!
147:
W-wait a minute. This sounds
serious. What's going on?
150:
That iron horse is running wild, and
our fair companion is trapped
aboard it!
153:
You two seem quite adept at riding
these contraptions. Could you lend
us a hand?
158: Leave it to us! We've got this!
161: My thanks! I shall repay you in kind!
173:
Your gratitude is unwarranted,
Stella. It was my lack of forethought
that led to this incident. If those men
hadn't—
176:
No, it was my own fault. But that is
not what I am referring to.
180:
I had a lot of fun today. Thank you
for that.
187:
Do you remember what I swore to
you and Alk?
193:
I swore on my pride as a dragon
slayer that together, we would build
a new future, no matter what that
future is. That much has not
changed.
196:
However, even if I am not needed as
a dragon slayer... I would not mind
being there for you two as a friend
either.
199:
In any case, our vacation is just
beginning. Are you ready for more
fun in the sun?
209:
Now... What would you like to do
tomorrow?
